Class LabeledGraphStringString

        • org.gradoop.flink.algorithms.fsm.dimspan.tuples.LabeledGraphStringString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class LabeledGraphStringString
extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple3<int[],String[],String[]>
    Minimalistic model of a string-labeled graph. f0: [sourceId_0,targetId_0,..,sourceId_n,targetId_k] f1: [vertexLabel_0,..,vertexLabel_j] f2: [edgeLabel_0,..,edgeLabel_k]
